{"tid":275121,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我係我個ex隻兵","createTime":"2017-06-07T19:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T20:54:53.000Z","uid":59712,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff3505b5f993887c96f25a1bea6391475f08563c","tid":275121,"uid":59712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:46:01.000Z","msg":"之前個故出左番外篇 你地睇左未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n估唔到上一個故反應都唔錯 希望大家繼續支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個故同上一個故得少少關連 冇睇過都唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過睇左就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我個ex係我其中一個sp</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/250766/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/250766/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n兵有好多種，步兵、水兵、騎兵⋯<br />\n<br />\n我係介乎係步兵同水兵中間，隨傳隨到，間唔中買下野比娘娘<br />\n<br />\n分左手仲肯做兵，因為我好想同番佢一齊<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都知如果佢係想同番我一齊就一早一齊左<br />\n<br />\n收得我做兵就一世都係兵<br />\n<br />\n不過人就係咁犯賤，點都覺得仲有少少希望"},{"pid":"4318ed44e0e81e9b2439a4e255184f609227659e","tid":275121,"uid":59712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:51:18.000Z","msg":"「唔好話我唔教精你啦。你想佢緊張你既話，你就要唔好緊張佢」Zero擺出一副專家既樣同我講<br />\n<br />\n我望住部電話個whatsapp chat room，再好無助咁望住Zero，「咁即係我唔好主動搵佢？」<br />\n<br />\n「緊係啦」<br />\n<br />\n「但我唔搵佢，佢一定唔會搵我架喎」我好迷茫咁碌番呢幾日既「對話」<br />\n<br />\n其實都係得我係到單機講野，稱唔上係對話<br />\n<br />\nZero嘆左一口氣，「咁你搵佢，佢有無覆你先？」<br />\n<br />\n我正想答佢個時，佢已經搶先一步講，「無呀嘛！咁你不如唔好再chur佢，等佢搵你仲好啦」<br />\n<br />\n「人好犯賤架。你日日都搵佢，佢咪覺得煩囉。你試下唔搵佢幾日，佢就會諗你做咩唔搵佢」Zero繼續用專家既口吻演講<br />\n<br />\n我又覺得佢講得幾有道理<br />\n<br />\n好似呀媽咁，佢日哦夜哦，你會覺得好煩；佢唔哦你，你又唔慣<br />\n<br />\n我用力咁捉實Zero對手，「好！我信哂你架啦，心靈大師！」<br />\n<br />\n佢好得戚咁笑左笑，「信我實無死」"},{"pid":"b6c64c9549bdd01eee34c192e88dd7963fe8f162","tid":275121,"uid":28873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T20:09:24.000Z","msg":"兵"},{"pid":"cb41a2df840f5c9a2f71cd976a10c04a639dbdf6","tid":275121,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T20:11:05.000Z","msg":"見到username就即刻入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e309d5d310424590e06aa68a02141616e323112c","tid":275121,"uid":88503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T22:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到username就即刻入黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n+1<br />\n望到心靈個名心又開始拿住拿住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950ca65b6781dcba987a3e4c412b2f4ed4938e16","tid":275121,"uid":105541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:39:42.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於有另一個故事<br />\n樓主加油寫故呀<br />\n皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db9196daf870158b396f36da3ee9dc0e207f77d5","tid":275121,"uid":89798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T18:42:29.000Z","msg":"Lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d9a194f144b86acfedee208538cf79c22cafc4","tid":275121,"uid":60966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:27:52.000Z","msg":"冇啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d02d9ec3f199b24f4ca3eb4a4ed5835748f287","tid":275121,"uid":28873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:25:36.000Z","msg":"棄PO"},{"pid":"f01c244311c98dd65ce64ff45212160a18638de8","tid":275121,"uid":120422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"LM 文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff814a0f6cb3d9e659954dbf170b16e4862d38a","tid":275121,"uid":36504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316d764207ea5b7a8c197cde34e9a42598af7258","tid":275121,"uid":81762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T03:58:06.000Z","msg":"好想瘋狂幫樓主打句號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635e3bfc0e1e706d868612f6ca1ed52338e103db","tid":275121,"uid":105506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T16:50:00.000Z","msg":"咁如果對方都一直唔搵你<br />\n咁點"},{"pid":"188a91264aa79b9ff224e06607e1b3cf6c176d84","tid":275121,"uid":6674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T02:36:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"dd23d115470a1fe15c75a3f2ed57026ac98afb96","tid":275121,"uid":119454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T12:18:46.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8c0b9c5f97361b2b77a4f3a9df50160f7ec909","tid":275121,"uid":59712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:54:08.000Z","msg":"Sorry之前停左無繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家繼續寫仲有無人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0ebf1e1c54b193a666ea9e4acc30ba85c4548b","tid":275121,"uid":59712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T20:54:53.000Z","msg":"聽完Zero講，我已經有兩三日無搵過Hailey<br />\n<br />\n我總係會成日望住部電話，希望佢會有一秒諗起我，然後搵我<br />\n<br />\n但我知呢件事係無可能發生<br />\n<br />\n我每晚都好掙扎，要忍住唔搵佢<br />\n<br />\n好似人地有煙癮咁，要介煙從來唔係一件容易既事<br />\n<br />\n得不到的永遠在騷動 被偏愛的都有恃無恐<br />\n<br />\n夜晚自己一個人訓係床到，總係特別多野諗<br />\n<br />\n諗起以前同Hailey一齊既回憶，後悔一齊個時冇對佢再好啲<br />\n<br />\n如果個時對佢再好啲，佢係咪就唔會同我分手<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，電話彈左一個通知出黎：<br />\nhaileyyau剛剛張貼了1張相片。<br />\n<br />\n我眼定定咁望住左個電話螢幕十秒<br />\n<br />\n<em>「喂，我po左相你做咩唔like呀？」Hailey嬲爆爆咁問我<br />\n<br />\n「我點知你po左相⋯」我好無辜咁望住佢<br />\n<br />\n「搞錯！」佢一手搶左我部電話，㩒左入ig到，「拿！幫你開左我個帖子啦。你以後要第一個like我張相！」<br />\n<br />\n我笑住咁摸佢個頭，「如果有人快手過我呢？」<br />\n<br />\n佢好認真咁諗左陣，「咁⋯都係你既錯！」</em><br />\n<br />\n以前同Hailey打鬧既場面係腦海閃過，可惜都係以前既事<br />\n<br />\n我習慣性即刻㩒入ig，想like張相個刻，隻手指停左係到<br />\n<br />\n我仲有必要做第一個like既人咩⋯<br />\n<br />\n佢係我既全世界，而我係佢既世界連一粒灰塵都比唔上"}]}